===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|univers|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|universum||all things, as a whole, the universe|lang=la}}, neuter of {{term|universus||all together, whole, entire, collective, general, literally turned or combined into one|lang=la}}, from {{term|uni-|lang=la}}, combining form of {{term|unus||one|lang=la}} + {{term|versus||turned|lang=la}}, perfect passive participle of {{term|verto|verto|I turn|lang=la}}.

